  src/types.ts        — written fresh (structural GroupSessionLike + event/state
                        types; normative API surface). SPDX: AGPL-3.0-or-later.
  src/errors.ts       — written fresh (error taxonomy). SPDX: AGPL-3.0-or-later.
  src/storage.ts      — written fresh (closed_group:{id}:* storage schema +
                        InMemoryGroupStorage). SPDX: AGPL-3.0-or-later.
  src/keygen.ts       — written fresh (group address ed→x25519 + x25519
                        encryption keypair generation, plan §2.1; noble).
